data.description: What a jewel!  Nestled in a peaceful rural community, this charming homes offers a blend of modern comfort and tranquil living.  Situated on a generous 2.44 acre lot, the property features 4 bedrooms, all with private baths and walk in closets.  Discover a beautifully updated kitchen with an open concept design, large island and breakfast nook, perfect for entertaining.  One of the standout features is the double sided fireplace, providing warmth and ambiance to both the living area and formal dining/sitting area. The upstairs gameroom could also provide a 5th bedroom if needed. If you enjoy the outdoors, you will fall in love with the spacious covered front porch and patio. With a quick commute to Owasso or Oologah Lake, all your needs are minutes away. Don't miss this opportunity to make this your new home sweet home!
